Package uk.ac.bristol.star.feather

Interface Summary
BufAccess Basic interface for access to a potentially large byte storage array.
ColStat Characterises what was written by a column writer.
FeatherColumnWriter Supplies the metadata and byte stream associated with serializing a column of a Feather-format table.
Reader<T> Reads a value from a given slot of a feather column.
 

Class Summary
AbstractColumnWriter Partial FeatherColumnWriter implementation that handles generic aspects including writing the optional validity mask.
BooleanRandomWriter Partial FeatherColumnWriter for random access boolean columns.
Buf Provides methods to work with a potentially large byte buffer.
BufMapper Provides memory-mapped random access to potentially large files.
BufUtils Miscellaneous utilities for working with bytes.
Decoder<T> Turns feather-encoded byte data into typed data values.
FeatherColumn Represents a column in a readable Feather-format table.
FeatherTable Presents a readable view of a feather-format table on disk.
FeatherType Enumeration class for Feather-format type constants.
FeatherWriter Can write table data to a Feather-format file.
NumberRandomWriter FeatherColumnWriter implementations for random access primitive-valued columns.
VariableLengthRandomWriter Partial FeatherColumnWriter implementation for random access variable-length data types.
